[I] A software synthesiser emulating pre-GM MIDI devices

[T] A multi-platform software synthesiser emulating (somewhat inaccurately)
[T] pre-GM MIDI devices such as the Roland MT-32, CM-32L, CM-64 and LAPC-I.
[T] In no way endorsed by or affiliated with Roland Corp.

